CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1963, pg. 19, reads: "1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama Exhibitors who were not shown on last week's picture page are shown here... 4. Coca-Cola: Jim Lewis, sales representative, and Ruby Ellison, hostess... All Home-A-Rama Photos (Including last week's) by Charles (Teenie) Harris."
TitMainTitle: Jim Lewis and Ruby Ellison standing behind Coca-Cola booth, with Coca-Cola curtains hanging back wall, at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
